lead_paragraph: A group seeking to build a new soccer stadium in St. Louis postponed its Tuesday meeting with a state finance board, one day after Missouri's governor-elect expressed strong opposition to public financing for the project.

headline.print_headline: Group Postpones Meeting Over St. Louis Soccer Stadium Plan
